  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to correlate the alimentary consistencies and deglutition
      disorders in children with cerebral palsy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Cross-sectional and quantitative study with sample consisted of 50 children with cerebral
      palsy. The data collection consisted in detection of the main dysphagic manifestations in
      different consistency of food and types of cerebral palsy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
